tsl:SchemeName.tsl:Name: LU:Supervision/Accreditation Status List of certification services from Certification Service Providers, which are supervised/accredited by the referenced Scheme Operator’s Member State for compliance with the relevant provisions laid down in Directive 1999/93/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 December 1999 on a Community framework for electronic signatures.

tsl:PolicyOrLegalNotice.tsl:TSLLegalNotice: The applicable legal framework for the present TSL implementation of the Trusted List of supervised/accredited Certification Service Providers for Luxembourg is Directive 1999/93/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 December 1999 on a Community framework for electronic signatures and its implementation in Luxembourgish laws. The accreditation scheme for all CSPs issuing qualified, non-qualified certificates, or other services related to electronic signature is based upon the Law of 14 August 2000, and Grand-Ducal Regulations of 1st June 2001 and 21 December 2004.
